Phoebe::She did? Why?
;她退出了? 为什么?

42
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:31,700
Monica::I made her.
;我叫她这么做的

43
00:03:32,300 --> 00:03:37,000
Monica::Steel drums don't really say elegant wedding. Nor does Margery's overwhelming scent.
;钢鼓和高雅的婚礼不太搭调， 而且Margery的体味太浓了

44
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:41,000
Phoebe::Hey! She will shower when Tibet is free.
