Phoebe::Rehearse it.
;先演习一下吧

51
00:04:08,300 --> 00:04:10,000
Ross::Hi.
;嗨

52
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,700
Mike::Thanks for coming, you guys.
;真高兴你们都来了

53
