Ross::That is why.
;没错

56
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,300
Phoebe::So, Rach, where is Emma?
;好了, Rach, Emma呢?

57
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:25,500
Rachel::Oh, Monica made me send her to my mother's.
;哦, Monica让我把她送到我妈那里去了

58
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:28,900
Rachel::Apparently, babies and weddings don't mix.
;显然，婴儿和婚礼可掺合不到一块儿

59
00:04:28,900 --> 00:04:32,100
Monica::Are you still crying about your damn baby?
;你还在为你那烦人的小家伙哭哭啼啼的?

60
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:36,600
Monica::Phoebs, you gotta keep the line moving. Remember, 20 seconds per person.
