126
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:25,400
Mike::Hey, unless we move in with you, dad.
;嘿, 除非我们搬去跟你一起住, 爸爸

127
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:27,900
Joey::Strike 3.
;第三拳

128
00:08:27,900 --> 00:08:31,900
Joey::You only get one more, Mike.
;你只有最后一次机会了，Mike

129
